column5: a real nice pike 43 inches length 29 inches in girth 100 feet of ice off the shoreline not what i was expecting!!! had to fish some different spots than used to. found a few shallower shoals out in the middle of the lake where i hooked into this big guy.
ya got great pike up that way and thats for sure a dandy  Hawg Hunter
thats a beauty jackfish! Way to go man!  Hawk
That there's a nomadic pike!  Nice fish.  Congrats!  cheers HD
Great report and pic BassAsin  Congratulation on that fine catch Thanks for sharing Leechman
Nice pike, congrats !!!  Huge head on her !!!
awesome pike!  through the ice? must have been fun!
Nice  fish dude. Nice and clean!
no out of the boat had to break through a couple inches for quite a piece to get out to the open water
That there is a Monster WaterWolf............Biggest I've seen in a long time

ice shack is 12x16 turns into camp in the off season at a buddies property. dual action!!!
